<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>We found a great match: {{matchName}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background: #fafaf9;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo-text {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #a07855;
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #525252;
    }
    .match-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e4;
    }
    .match-name {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .match-score {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #a07855;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .shared-interest {
      background: #fef3c7;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #78350f;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .reason {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #525252;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .button-group {
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .button-accept {
      background: #a07855;
      color: #ffffff !important;
    }
    .button-accept:hover {
      background: #8a6547;
    }
    .button-pass {
      background: #f5f5f4;
      color: #525252 !important;
    }
    .button-pass:hover {
      background: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e4;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #737373;
    }
    .privacy-note {
      background: #f0fdf4;
      border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #14532d;
    }
    .expires {
      background: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="logo-text">grove</div>
    </div>

    <h1>We found a great match for you!</h1>

    <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

    <p>Based on your interests and what you're working on, we think you'd connect well with this person:</p>

    <div class="match-card">
      <div class="match-name">{{matchName}}</div>
      <div class="match-score">{{score}}% match</div>

      <div class="shared-interest">
        <strong>Shared interest:</strong> {{sharedInterest}}
      </div>

      <div class="reason">
        {{reason}}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-note">
      Privacy first: They won't know you saw this unless you both choose to connect.
    </div>

    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #1a1a1a; margin-top: 30px;">
      <strong>What would you like to do?</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="button-group">
      <a href="{{acceptUrl}}" class="button button-accept">I'm interested</a>
      <a href="{{passUrl}}" class="button button-pass">Not for me</a>
    </div>

    <div class="expires">
      This match expires in <strong>7 days</strong>. Take your time!
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        <strong>Grove</strong> â€“ Professional connection matching<br>
        This email was sent to {{recipientEmail}}
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #a3a3a3;">
        These introductions are sent to help you discover meaningful professional connections.
        You can adjust your preferences anytime in settings.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
